description: There's a new Sheriff in town, and his name is Cody Cummings. He's been riding all day through the Wild West, and now he's settled in for sundown in this little one horse town. Now Cody can sling a six-shooter with the best of them, but truth be told, he's really much more fond of using the pistol in his pants. Watch as he unwinds from the long hard day, before letting off his rifle in a massive explosion.Enjoy!
title: COWBOY CODY
